org.lenskit.results

Class AbstractResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lenskit.results.AbstractResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Result, KeyedObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicResult, ItemItemResult, OrdRecRatingPredictor.FullResult, RankBlendResult, UserUserResult

    public abstract class AbstractResult
extends Object
implements Result, KeyedObject

    Base class for basic result types. It provides storage for the ID and score, as well as helper methods for hashing and equality checking. This type does not directly enforce immutability, but subclasses should be immutable.
